content:
Sure! Here are some Latin-based words that could work as names for a baby milestone app:

1. Cresco (meaning "to grow")
2. Progressio (meaning "progress")
3. Evolutio (meaning "evolution")
4. Avantia (meaning "advancement")
5. Primus Passus (meaning "first steps")
6. Flos (meaning "flower" or "bloom")
7. Lux (meaning "light" or "brightness")
8. Novus Ordo (meaning "new order")
9. Veritas (meaning "truth")
10. Scientia (meaning "knowledge")
